        <Parent_String>aniline dye [300013094], synthetic dye [300013088], dye by composition or origin [300013031], dye [300013029], colorant (material) [300013026], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
